headline: These Were the 2 Worst-Performing Stocks in the S&P 500 Over the Last Month
summary: The S&P 500 is hovering near an all-time high as investors have brushed off concerns about tariffs.  Enphase Energy tumbled recently on signs that solar credits could be eliminated.  Brown-Forman posted another quarter of weak results, due in part to pressure from tariffs.
